==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
Probably from a derivative of the alternate of [[πίνω]] (compare [[πότος]])

===Pronunciation===
*ποταμός / potamos / pot-am-os'

===Noun===
'''ποταμός'''

# a [[current]], [[brook]] or freshet (as drinkable), that is, running water: - [[flood]], [[river]], [[stream]], [[water]].

